| Feature               | Row Store Index                   | Column Store Index                                 |
| --------------------- | --------------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------- |
| **Data layout**       | Stores full rows together         | Stores columns separately                          |
| **Best for**          | OLTP (transactions, updates)      | OLAP (analytics, reporting)                        |
| **Query speed**       | Fast for small lookups            | Fast for large scans/aggregations                  |
| **Compression**       | Limited                           | Very high (columns compress well)                  |
| **Write performance** | Strong (rows updated easily)      | Slower (updating columnar storage is costly)       |
| **Examples**          | PostgreSQL default B-tree indexes | SQL Server Columnstore Index, ClickHouse, BigQuery |
